stickersOnItem: [{'stickerType': 4, 'stickerText': ['How i cook being a homeless teenager', 'I bought this cooker at walmart for about 15 dollars its really worth it \nI plug it in on a outlet i found at a park', 'I take water from the water fountain in a bottle and i pour it in this pot it was 3 dollars from the 99 cent store', 'These hotdogs were a dollar from the 99 cent store lets open them and chop them up', 'The water should be at a boil by now so lets get out the noodles', 'These noodles were a dollar at dollar tree so i take a handful of them and split them in half and put them in a pot', 'There done boiling lets drain them', 'This pasta sauce was a dollar at 99 cent store so lets put it into the noodles', 'I take the hotdogs that i cut and put it with the noodles to', 'Stir it all up', 'Get water from the water fountain for balance', 'A plastic untensal you can get a any store', 'And enjoy follow for more:)']}]
